      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 10px;">Last Updated: March 8, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ANSWER CAPSULE: Quick Reference -->
  <section style="padding: 32px 1.5rem; background: #f0f7ff; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;"><strong>Angel Bail Bonds provides 24/7 bail bond services for Lincoln County, Oklahoma. Lincoln County Jail is located at 811 Manvel Ave, Suite 14, Chandler, OK 74834. Call (405) 614-3000 to begin the bail process. The jail phone number is (405) 258-1191 ext. 294. Lincoln County Jail has a capacity of 128 inmates. Most inmates are released 1-4 hours after the bond is posted. We accept cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, Venmo, and offer financing.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FACILITY + STEPS — combined, two-column -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: white;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px;">

      <!-- Left: Jail Facility Details -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">Lincoln County Jail Facility Details</h2>
        <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 0.9rem; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600; width: 120px;">Address</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">811 Manvel Ave, Ste 14, Chandler, OK 74834</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Jail Phone</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);"><a href="tel:+14052581191" style="color: var(--blue);">(405) 258-1191 ext. 294</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Non-Emergency</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);"><a href="tel:+14052589933" style="color: var(--blue);">(405) 258-9933</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Capacity</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">128 inmates</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Sheriff</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">Charlie Dougherty</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Visitation</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">M-F 10 AM - 3 PM (on-site, scheduled 24hr ahead)</td>
