            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">Daily 6:00 AM - 10:00 PM</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">County Seat</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">Chandler, Oklahoma</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: How to Get Bail Bond -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">How to Post Bail in Lincoln County</h2>
        <ol style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">1</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Call Angel Bail Bonds</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">(405) 614-3000 · Available 24/7/365</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">2</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">We confirm inmate details</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">Charges, bail amount, booking number from Lincoln County Jail</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">3</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Pay the premium & sign paperwork</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">Cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, Venmo · Financing available</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">4</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Bond is posted at the jail</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">We travel to Chandler or handle remotely by phone</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Your loved one is released</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">Typical processing: 1-4 hours after bond is posted</span></div>
          </li>
